name: Digitize Paper Forms
description: Paper forms are the enemy of productivity. They exist today as an unnecessary intermediate between humans and machines only to be manually inputted into databases. Our goal is to develop a machine learning model for converting any paper form into an electronic interface capable of capturing user input for fields unique to the original paper form.
